 "werwer", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/werwer", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a88b83b75a31ee203c47cd7cc38ce1f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a88b83b75a31ee203c47cd7cc38ce1f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a88b83b75a31ee203c47cd7cc38ce1f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1664839684, "last_modified": 1707300070}, "last_reply_by": "saranz", "last_touched": 1722947462, "title": "初学者应该选择哪种双拼方案？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1062757", "created": 1722869463, "deleted": 0, "content": "用全拼一打快了总是把顺序按错，想要学习一下双拼，有没有必要性呢？\r\n看了一个相同话题的帖子，简单统计了一下回帖，小鹤具有压倒性的推荐率\r\n排在第二位的微软，主要的推荐理由是覆盖面，各平台初始设定，但我觉得这不是很重要，缺点是占用；\r\n自然码，网上的说法是接近于全拼的排布，所以易上手，我对比了一下微软，布局很接近，且没有占用；\r\n所以从易学性，合理顺手性的角度考虑，初学者到底应该选用哪种呢？\r\n--------------------------\r\n小鹤\t50.82%\r\n微软\t11.48%\r\n自然码\t9.84%\r\n拼音加加\t8.20%\r\n小鹤音形\t8.20%\r\n智能 ABC\t4.92%\r\n搜狗\t3.28%\r\n两笔输入法\t1.64%\r\n辜氏 2 低重码\t1.64%", "content_rendered": "用全拼一打快了总是把顺序按错，想要学习一下双拼，有没有必要性呢？<br />看了一个相同话题的帖子，简单统计了一下回帖，小鹤具有压倒性的推荐率<br />排在第二位的微软，主要的推荐理由是覆盖面，各平台初始设定，但我觉得这不是很重要，缺点是占用；<br />自然码，网上的说法是接近于全拼的排布，所以易上手，我对比了一下微软，布局很接近，且没有占用；<br />所以从易学性，合理顺手性的角度考虑，初学者到底应该选用哪种呢？<br />--------------------------<br />小鹤\t50.82%<br />微软\t11.48%<br />自然码\t9.84%<br />拼音加加\t8.20%<br />小鹤音形\t8.20%<br />智能 ABC\t4.92%<br />搜狗\t3.28%<br />两笔输入法\t1.64%<br />辜氏 2 低重码\t1.64%", "last_modified": 1722942916, "replies": 85, "id": 1062757}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e57c/6b95/772_large.png?m=1646751663", "name": "github", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e57c/6b95/772_normal.png?m=1646751663", "title": "GitHub", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/github", "topics": 1113, "footer": "", "header": "A global place for programmers.", "title_alternative": "GitHub", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e57c/6b95/772_mini.png?m=1646751663", "stars": 653, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 772, "parent_node_name": "programmer"}, "member": {"id": 445155, "username": "n18255447846", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/n18255447846", "website": "https://ningtaostudy.cn", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0b4a34fe20399f98ec5464af511916b4?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0b4a34fe20399f98ec5464af511916b4?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0b4a34fe20399f98ec5464af511916b4?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1570521026, "last_modified": 1687754788}, "last_reply_by": "cnt2ex", "last_touched": 1722948667, "title": "github 强制 2fa，有什么替代的吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1062879", "created": 1722917840, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天逛 trending 发现跳出个强制 2fa 页面，反正也懒得弄，等于这个账号算废了，，，\r\n\r\n![2fa]( https://i.imgur.com/ahUKwVz.png)\r\n\r\n老哥们 git 仓库都存哪呢，分享下", "content_rendered": "<p>今天逛 trending 发现跳出个强制 2fa 页面，反正也懒得弄，等于这个账号算废了，，，</p>\n<p><img alt=\"2fa\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ahUKwVz.png\"/></p>\n<p>老哥们 git 仓库都存哪呢，分享下</p>\n", "last_modified": 1722928543, "replies": 74, "id": 1062879}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1630576706", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 1691, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706", "stars": 2825, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 324508, "username": "itskingname", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/itskingname", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5469/969b/324508_mini.png?m=1532149726", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5469/969b/324508_normal.png?m=1532149726", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5469/969b/324508_large.png?m=1532149726", "created": 1529883749, "last_modified": 1532149726}, "last_reply_by": "chaleaochexist", "last_touched": 1722947170, "title": "从不炒股的我来说说我观察到的一些股民的现象", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1062876", "created": 1722917461, "deleted": 0, "content": "我从来没有炒过股，也不懂股票的交易逻辑，但是我发现身边很多炒股的人买卖股票的方法非常玄学。\r\n\r\n1. 我一个叔叔，有一次给我介绍他的选股经验，看 K 线，K 线水平了多少厘米，接下来上涨就会涨多少厘米\r\n2. 这个 topic 下面其他帖子的楼主，他们坚信逢跌就买，跌 10%就买 20%，跌 20%就加仓 40%……再跌再买，越跌越买\r\n3. 全球股票大跌，所以接下来 A 股要涨了\r\n4. 还有些人，对他买的股票背后的公司完全不了解。公司做什么的，市场份额怎么样，有没有人事变动一概不知。\r\n5. ...\r\n\r\n\r\n我觉得他们的这些炒股方法毫无逻辑，根据我少有的经济学知识，买股票不应该是一看政府大环境，二看股票背后这个公司的发展和价值吗？ K 线横多少竖多少跟公司价值有什么关系？逢跌就买的人，不怕公司直接跌下市了？\r\n\r\n我没有嘲讽各位的意思，我只是觉得这些操作很玄学。有没有老司机能给我介绍一下这样做为什么会有用呢？", "content_rendered": "<p>我从来没有炒过股，也不懂股票的交易逻辑，但是我发现身边很多炒股的人买卖股票的方法非常玄学。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>我一个叔叔，有一次给我介绍他的选股经验，看 K 线，K 线水平了多少厘米，接下来上涨就会涨多少厘米</li>\n<li>这个 topic 下面其他帖子的楼主，他们坚信逢跌就买，跌 10%就买 20%，跌 20%就加仓 40%……再跌再买，越跌越买</li>\n<li>全球股票大跌，所以接下来 A 股要涨了</li>\n<li>还有些人，对他买的股票背后的公司完全不了解。公司做什么的，市场份额怎么样，有没有人事变动一概不知。</li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ol>\n<p>我觉得他们的这些炒股方法毫无逻辑，根据我少有的经济学知识，买股票不应该是一看政府大环境，二看股票背后这个公司的发展和价值吗？ K 线横多少竖多少跟公司价值有什么关系？逢跌就买的人，不怕公司直接跌下市了？</p>\n<p>我没有嘲讽各位的意思，我只是觉得这些操作很玄学。有没有老司机能给我介绍一下这样做为什么会有用呢？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1722917561, "replies": 66, "id": 1062876}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 63683, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 9049, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 634465, "username": "Inzufu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Inzufu", "website": "https://muna.uk", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "Lilac-milena", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e8a/951b/634465_mini.png?m=1700832337", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e8a/951b/634465_normal.png?m=1700832337", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e8a/951b/634465_large.png?m=1700832337", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e8a/951b/634465_xlarge.png?m=1700832337", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e8a/951b/634465_xlarge.png?m=1700832337", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6e8a/951b/634465_xlarge.png?m=1700832337", "created": 1686961054, "last_modified": 1700832337}, "last_reply_by": "IamUNICODE", "last_touched": 1722947409, "title": "感觉云端开发会是未来的趋势", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1062738", "created": 1722863999, "deleted": 0, "content": "之前用过 GitHub codespace 最近刚转用 Coding 在线 IDE ，两者体验都出奇的好，不用在机器上配置繁重的开发环境，还可以直接云端编译代码。\r\n同时在一定程度上也能保证安全性。对于开发者，未知的代码可以直接在云环境中运行测试；对于企业，应该能做到数据不落地，保证数据安全。\r\n此外云开发也不要求本地机器的性能，把一些重算力的任务放在服务器端进行，还能提高效率（开发效率和能源效率）。如果拿笔记本开发，即使设备丢了，只要及时登出会话，也不会造成数据泄露。\r\n\r\n这么看来谷歌的 Chrome OS 确实是一个挺有前瞻性的项目。", "content_rendered": "之前用过 GitHub codespace 最近刚转用 Coding 在线 IDE ，两者体验都出奇的好，不用在机器上配置繁重的开发环境，还可以直接云端编译代码。<br />同时在一定程度上也能保证安全性。对于开发者，未知的代码可以直接在云环境中运行测试；对于企业，应该能做到数据不落地，保证数据安全。<br />此外云开发也不要求本地机器的性能，把一些重算力的任务放在服务器端进行，还能提高效率（开发效率和能源效率）。如果拿笔记本开发，即使设备丢了，只要及时登出会话，也不会造成数据泄露。<br /><br />这么看来谷歌的 Chrome OS 确实是一个挺有前瞻性的项目。", "last_modified": 1722863999, "replies": 65, "id": 1062738}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 221708, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4220, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 662642, "username": "hello202311", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hello202311", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "tha816674@谷歌.com", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c6fda93eaebac1d96038370f3c7c8ba8?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c6fda93eaebac1d96038370f3c7c8ba8?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c6fda93eaebac1d96038370f3c7c8ba8?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1700030652, "last_modified": 1700030652}, "last_reply_by": "BoyBoy", "last_touched": 1722947404, "title": "长期不用风扇，选择循环扇还是风扇呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1062788", "created": 1722905117, "deleted": 0, "content": "长期不用风扇了，也没研究过风扇，不知道循环山和风扇之间应该选择哪种，看了一些资料说循环扇要配合空调使用，最近不想开空调，想要那种有自然风的，静音效果好些的，风的种类多的，有可以推荐的吗？谢谢", "content_rendered": "<p>长期不用风扇了，也没研究过风扇，不知道循环山和风扇之间应该选择哪种，看了一些资料说循环扇要配合空调使用，最近不想开空调，想要那种有自然风的，静音效果好些的，风的种类多的，有可以推荐的吗？谢谢</p>\n", "last_modified": 1722905117, "replies": 64, "id": 1062788}]